01:20:38.294 --> 01:20:40.004
Oprostite.

01:20:40.129 --> 01:20:42.506
Calle Don Tello?

01:20:42.589 --> 01:20:43.965
Marco, semkaj.

01:20:58.102 --> 01:20:59.728
Ne otežuj nam dela.

01:21:02.189 --> 01:21:03.398
Prosim.

